---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<section id="completeschedule" class="dark:bg-neutral-900">
	<div class="md:py-16 sm:px-4 mx-auto md:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-6xl">
		<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 lg:mb-14">
			<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold md:text-4xl md:leading-tight dark:text-white">Conference Book</h2>
			<p class="mt-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
				We are thrilled to be a platform for knowledge sharing and community building within the Bioinformatics field.
				We hope that this year's event will provide a great experience for everyone and help advance the future of
				Bioinformatics, both nationally and internationally.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
				<!-- Use flex to align buttons side by side -->
				<div class="mr-4">
					<!-- Container for the first button -->
					<a
						class="btn bg-primary-600"
						href="https://github.com/BioinformaticOpenDays/bods-website-2023/raw/main/public/BOD_Conference_Book.pdf"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener"
					>
						<Icon name="tabler:file-download" class="w-5 h-5 mr-1 -ml-1.5" /> Conference Book
					</a>
				</div>
				<div>
					<!-- Container for the second button -->
					<a
						class="btn bg-primary-600"
						href="https://github.com/BioinformaticOpenDays/bods-website-2023/raw/main/public/BOD_Abstract_Book.pdf"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener"
					>
						<Icon name="tabler:file-download" class="w-5 h-5 mr-1 -ml-1.5" /> Abstract Book
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="my-16">
				<p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
					Thank you for your participation and enthusiasm, and we look forward to seeing you at the XIII Edition of the
					Bioinformatics Open Days.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
					Kind regards, <br />The Organizing Committee of BOD 2024
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
